cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SE 

This paper proposes a formal framework for studying the design of verification mechanisms for data deletion requests in the context of machine learning as a service. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
